snippet.description:
Making fire with bamboo is a time-tested survival skill ‚Äî and yes, it still works!

Here‚Äôs what you need to know:
‚úî Use hard, dry bamboo ‚Äî yellow or slightly green is best.
‚ùå Avoid gray bamboo ‚Äî it‚Äôs been waterlogged and wears out too fast.
‚úî A bit damp? Just dry it in the sun or wipe it down.
‚úî Start rubbing slowly ‚Äî it helps warm the surface and push out moisture.
‚úî Sharper edges = better friction.
‚úî Save your energy ‚Äî once you smell burning, that‚Äôs your cue to speed up and press harder.
‚úî Smoke doesn‚Äôt mean fire yet ‚Äî keep going!
‚ö†Ô∏è Don‚Äôt forget to prepare a tinder nest in advance ‚Äî once the ember forms, gently place it inside to blow it into flame.

For this process I used my ROXON S803E Elite multitool ‚Äî super handy in the wild!

snippet.title: Kasalan, naudlot dahil si groom, ginayuma diumano ni bride? | Kapuso Mo, Jessica Soho
snippet.description:
Aired (March 16, 2025):

KASALAN SA CAGAYAN DE ORO CITY, NAUDLOT DAHIL SI GROOM, GINAYUMA DIUMANO NI BRIDE? 

Paalala: Maging disente sa mga komento.

Simple pero elegante ang set up ng civil wedding sa Cagayan de Oro City sa Mindanao. Pero ang groom, biglang nag-backout?!

Ang lalaking dapat ikakasal, ginayuma lang diumano ng babae!

Natauhan lang daw ang groom, matapos itong sabuyan‚Ä¶ ng asin!

Ano nga ba ang totoo sa mga kumalat na kuwento? 

Panoorin ang video. #KMJS
